Crypto News App

This app provides an upto date list of news on all things Crypto and Bitcoin.

This app pulls data from the News Api website using its open platform API. If you are interested in Bitcoin or Crypto currencies, this is a great way of staying upto date, or alternatively searching for relevant news.

Prerequisites

Android SDK v29 Android Build Tools v29.0.3

This app uses Loaders to manage tasks in the background off the UI
